    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.什麼是企業家精神(Entrepreneurship)？<br>2.你的創業想法是什麼？這個想法將如何影響市場的變化？<br>3.你的創業計畫是什麼？<br>4.你想如何執行你的創業計畫？<br>",
        "en": "1.What is entrepreneurship? <br>2.Develop your startup idea: what do you bring to the market?  <br>3.What is your business plan? <br>4.How do you make it work? <br>"
    },
